layout.p:
Columns: 2;
                                                  ruled lines: 24;
                                                  written lines: 24; Ezekiel, Amos and Jonah open a new column, and Isaiah commences a new leaf. The chapters have been numbered in ordinary figures by a later hand, partly in ink and partly in pencil. There is number of masoretic notes at the end of each book. The beginning and end of Hafṭarot have occasionally been marked in the margin by a later hand.
